Sum of Even Numbers till N
Send Feedback
Given a number N, print sum of all even numbers from 1 to N.
Input Format :
Integer N
Output Format :
Required Sum 
Sample Input 1 :
 6
Sample Output 1 :
12

code-

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){

	int N;
	int i =2;
	int sum=0;
	cin>>N;
	while(i<=N)
	{
         sum=sum+i;
		 i=i+2;
    }
        cout << sum;
}